
var1 = value
var2 = $(var1) another      saves var1 in var2 as a dynamic variable and appends another
var1 := different           replaces the value priviously stored in it
var3 ?= first!              stores the value only if there was none before
var3 += secooond!!          appends the value

$@                          target
$(@D)                       target's directory
$<                          first prerequisite
$^                          all prerequisites

-                           ignore error if one occurs
@                           won't print the command in the makefile to the terminal